Package: iki.dataclim
Type: Package
Title: Consistency, Homogeneity and Summary Statistics of
        Climatological Data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-07-18
Author: Boris Orlowsky 
Maintainer: Boris Orlowsky <boris@climate-babel.org>
URL: www.climate-babel.org
Description: The package offers an S4 infrastructure to store climatological
  station data of various temporal aggregation scales. In-built quality
  control and homogeneity tests follow the methodology from the European
  Climate Assessment & Dataset project. Wrappers for climate indices
  defined by the Expert Team on Climate Change Detection and Indices
  (ETCCDI), a quick summary of important climate statistics and climate
  diagram plots provide a fast overview of climatological
  characteristics of the station.   
License: GPL-3
Copyright: Boris Orlowsky <boris@climate-babel.org>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: methods, zoo, lubridate, climdex.pcic (>= 1.1-1), PCICt
Packaged: 2014-09-18 20:02:19 UTC; oboris
NeedsCompilation: no
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2014-09-19 10:33:43
